BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:vDndf_orhDAlTvKuFRW8K
SUMMARY:IMPROV 100 WEDNESDAYS - Intro to Improv: Say Yes!\\\, SPRING'26
DTSTAMP:20260326T004307Z
DTSTART:20260325T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:You are registered. Welcome!\\nThank you for registering for th
	is eight-week course at Unexpected Productions Improv. We’re excited to ha
	ve you join us. \\nPlease read the details below carefully. This informati
	on is important.\\nTime and Dates: Wednesdays for eight (8) weeks\\\, from
	 March 25 to May 23\\\, 7pm to 9:30pm \\nImportant Attendance Note\\nAtten
	dance at the first session is mandatory\\\, as it sets the agenda for the 
	entire quarter.\\nIf you think you may miss the first class\\\, we strongl
	y recommend registering for the next quarter instead. \\nLocation: 5700 6t
	h Ave St\\\, Suite 109\\\, Umbrella Room\\\, Seattle\\\, WA 98108\\nClass 
	Details\\n• Maximum Students: 16\\n• Cost: $295\\n• Age Requirement: 18+ \
	\nCancellation Policy\\nIf you must cancel before the first class\\\, we c
	an offer credit toward the same level class next quarter.\\nWe are unable 
	to offer refunds. If you cancel after the first class\\\, we cannot issue 
	credit for a future class and cannot offer refunds.\\nIf you have question
	s before the first class\\\, please contact us at school@unexpectedproduct
	ions.org \\nWe look forward to working with you and can’t wait to get star
	ted.\\nImprov classes are physically active and often involve movement\\\,
	 standing\\\, and high-energy exercises\\\, so staying hydrated is importa
	nt. \\nWe recommend the following:\\n• Comfortable clothing that allows fo
	r easy movement\\n• Comfortable shoes\\\, as you will likely be standing a
	nd moving for extended periods\\n• A notebook and pen\\\, if you would lik
	e to take notes on techniques or exercises\\n• A water bottle (some locati
	ons do not have water fountains)\\n• A “Yes\\\, And” attitude. A willingne
	ss to participate\\\, take risks\\\, and be brave is the most important th
	ing to bring\n\nhttps://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/improv-100-wed
	nesdays-intro-to-improv-say-yes-spring26/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/improv-100-wednesdays-intro
	-to-improv-say-yes-spring26/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions Improv School ISSAQUAH/EASTSIDE\\\, 1315 NW
	 Mall Street\\\, Suite 4\\\, Issaquah\\\, WA\\\, 98108\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:vArX4r9bINmruXFJkl_tJ
SUMMARY:Duo Comedy Showcase 2026
DTSTAMP:20260326T004307Z
DTSTART:20260325T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Seattle’s one and only open mic dedicated to two-person improv 
	teams! Every week at Unexpected Productions\\\, two-person teams take the 
	stage to create hilarious\\\, fast-paced\\\, totally unscripted comedy rig
	ht before your eyes. No scripts\\\, no safety nets—just pure improv magic.
	 \\nAt Duos\\\, everyone shines. Newer performers sharpen their game. Seas
	oned improvisers experiment\\\, take risks\\\, and get wonderfully weird. 
	The results? Quick-witted scenes\\\, surprising twists\\\, and bold choice
	s that feel impossible until you watch them happen live. \\nWhether you dr
	eam of being the next Key & Peele\\\, Tina Fey & Amy Poehler\\\, or a chao
	tic tag-team like Deadpool & Wolverine\\\, this is your chance to take the
	 mic and run with it. All experience levels are welcome. Bring a friend\\\
	, form a team\\\, and give Seattle a show they won’t forget. To sign up yo
	ur duo\\\, email duoshowcase@gmail.com. \\nLooking for a midweek serotonin
	 boost? Watching the show is just as fun as performing in it. Grab a seat\
	\\, grab a friend\\\, and discover why Unexpected Productions is the home 
	of Seattle improv.\n\nhttps://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/duo-come
	dy-showcase-2026/2026-03-25/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/duo-comedy-showcase-2026/20
	26-03-25/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
